# Security Best Practices for XRM Toolbox Usage

## ✅ 1. Use Read-Only Access When Possible
- If running reports, use **read-only access** instead of full admin permissions.

## ✅ 2. Backup Data Before Bulk Updates
- Always **export records to Excel** before modifying data.

## ✅ 3. Validate Metadata Report Before Using It
- Metadata reports should be **validated** before applying changes.

## ✅ 4. Ensure Plugin Authenticity
- Install plugins **only from the XRM Toolbox Plugin Store**.

